    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3 due to single-condition testing; this shortfall is accepted given the COU is explicitly bounded to the ASTM F1717 standard test configuration and the regulatory decision (510(k) substantial equivalence) does not require multi-condition generalization. All three QoIs pass the pre-specified E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criterion. Model credibility is sufficient to support submission.",
